biography.value:
Renacyt researcher and inventor recognized in Peru and the World. Doctor in Systems Engineering at the National University Federico Villarreal (Graduated), Doctorate in Education, Master in Electronic Sciences with a mention in Automation and Control at the National University of Callao (Graduated), Master in Educational Administration at the University Cesar Vallejo.
Robotics and Artificial Intelligence courses applied to biomedical at UVM Mexico, Academic mobility: Immersive Smart Campus & Smart Cities Innovation Program – Facens Brazil;
Experience in the industrial field for more than 20 years and as a Teacher in various Universities and Technological Institutes for more than 15 years, line of research in the field of Systems Engineering, Electronics, Mechatronics and Education. Teacher, advisor and thesis jury.
